<package project="Mer:Trunk:Base" name="ConsoleKit">
  <title>System daemon for tracking users, sessions and seats</title>
  <description>ConsoleKit is a system daemon for tracking what users are logged
into the system and how they interact with the computer (e.g.
which keyboard and mouse they use).

It provides asynchronous notification via the system message bus.

</description>
  <url>http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/ConsoleKit</url>
</package>